<txt_Description1><![CDATA[
        다음은 안전하고 건강한 호주 여행을 위한 자세한 정보를 제공하는 사이트입니다:
        <br />
        <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 관세 및 국경보호청(Australian Government Customs and Border Protection): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=customs');" target="_blank" href="http://www.customs.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.customs.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 검역 및 검사 서비스(The Australian Quarantine and Inspection Service): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=daff');" target="_blank" href="http://www.daff.gov.au/aqis"><span style="color: #000000;">www.daff.gov.au/aqis</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 보건부(Australian Department of Health and Ageing): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=health');" target="_blank" href="http://www.health.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.health.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 안보국(Australian National Security): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=nationalsecurity');" target="_blank" href="http://www.nationalsecurity.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.nationalsecurity.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 메디케어(Medicare Australia): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=medicareaustralia');" target="_blank" href="http://www.medicareaustralia.gov.au/public/migrants/visitors/index.jsp"><span style="color: #000000;">www.medicareaustralia.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>긴급 의료(Health Emergency): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=healthemergency');" target="_blank" href="http://www.healthemergency.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.healthemergency.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>장애인을 위한 호주 여행: <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=nican);" target="_blank" href="http://www.nican.com.au">www.nican.com.au</a> or <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=australiaforall');" target="_blank" href="http://www.australiaforall.com"><span style="color: #000000;">www.australiaforall.com</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주의 국립 공원과 야생지대: <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=environment');" target="_blank" href="http://www.environment.gov.au/parks"><span style="color: #000000;">www.environment.gov.au/parks</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 기상청(Australian Government Bureau of Meteorology): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=bom');" target="_blank" href="http://www.bom.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.bom.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 정부 재난 관리: <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=em');" target="_blank" href="http://www.em.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.em.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>똑똑한 자외선 차단법: <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=sunsmart');" target="_blank" href="http://www.sunsmart.com.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.sunsmart.com.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>호주 암 협회(Cancer Council Australia): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=cancer');" target="_blank" href="http://www.cancer.org.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.cancer.org.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>서프 라이프 세이빙 오스트레일리아(Surf Life Saving Australia): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=sls');" target="_blank" href="http://www.sls.com.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.sls.com.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>다이빙 산업 협회(Diving Industry Association): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=diveindustry);" target="_blank" href="http://www.diveindustry.com.au">www.diveindustry.com.au</a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
